an><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">sumTreeLen</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">start</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> sum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n    arr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">forEach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">elem</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>elem <span class=\"token operator\">></span> start<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> sum <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> elem <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> start\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> sum <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">M</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>이분 탐색을 위해서 L, R에 초기값을 줄 때, 반드시 L은 0, R은 필요한 나무의 길이의 최댓값인 2000000000을 주어야 한다.</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[boj] 2805. 나무 자르기 (node.js)","date":"220210 Thu","description":"이분 탐색 (Binary Search)"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/BOJ-node-js/BOJ-1011/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[boj] 1011. Fly me to the Alpha Centauri (node.js)"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/03-System_Program_1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"반효경 [운영체제] 3. System Structure & Program Execution 1"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"a4